What Euskara needs
Clear terms
Direct language
Immediate logic
Removal of ambiguity
How to communicate with Euskara
Define your terms early
Be specific, not symbolic
Break ideas into clean steps
Answer the question they actually asked
What not to do
Don’t speak vaguely or metaphorically when clarity is needed
Don’t bury your point in narrative
Don’t expect them to “infer” your meaning
How to support them
Give them clarity.
They will give you precision.

